                    ],
                    "stepSolveAnswerUnits": "m",
                    "stepConcepts": [],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "fdd0a2eb253f44aa884aa",
                    "stepText": "Now, analyze the deceleration phase where the train slows down from $!$30 \\ m/s$!$ to rest in $!$10 \\ s$!$. This again forms a triangle on the graph. Using the appropriate triangle area formula, compute the distance during deceleration.",
