                    "stepSolveAnswerUnits": "m",
                    "stepConcepts": [],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "25176780ee63435da4733",
                    "stepText": "Finally, add the distances from all three phases (acceleration, constant speed, and deceleration) to determine the total distance travelled by the train. What is the sum of these distances?",
